---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import "../styles/privacy.scss";
const pageTitle = "privacy";
---

<BaseLayout pageTitle={pageTitle}>
    <div class="privacy-policy">
        <div id="logo">
            <img src="logo.webp" alt="" />
        </div>
        <div class="block">
            <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
        </div>
        <p class="updated">Last updated: March 8, 2026</p>

        <p>
            Thank you for visiting <strong>ImpulseLog</strong>. We respect your
            privacy and are committed to protecting any information you may
            share while using this website. This Privacy Policy explains how
            information may be collected, used, and safeguarded when you access
            our blog.
        </p>

        <p>
            ImpulseLog is a science and education blog built using modern web
            technologies and hosted on a secure cloud platform. The purpose of
            this website is to provide educational articles related to physics,
            science, and technology.
        </p>

        <h2>1. Personal Information</h2>
        <p>
            Users can freely access all content on this website without creating
            an account or logging in. We do not require personal information for
            reading articles.
        </p>

        <p>
            However, if you choose to contact us through the contact form, you
            may voluntarily provide information such as:
        </p>

        <ul>
            <li>Your name</li>
            <li>Your email address</li>
            <li>Your message</li>
        </ul>

        <p>
            Our contact form is powered by
            <a
                href="https://formsubmit.co/"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer">FormSubmit</a
            >, a third-party service that securely forwards messages to our
            email address. This information is used only to respond to your
            inquiry and is not stored on our servers.
        </p>

        <p>
            We do not sell, rent, or share personal information with third
            parties.
        </p>

        <h2>2. Hosting and Technical Information</h2>
        <p>
            This website is hosted on
            <a
                href="https://vercel.com/"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer">Vercel</a
            >. Like most hosting providers, basic technical information may
            automatically be collected for security, analytics, and performance
            monitoring.
        </p>

        <p>This information may include:</p>

        <ul>
            <li>IP address</li>
            <li>Browser type and version</li>
            <li>Device type and operating system</li>
            <li>Pages visited</li>
            <li>Date and time of access</li>
        </ul>

        <p>
            This data is used only for technical and security purposes and is
            not used by us to personally identify visitors.
        </p>

        <h2>3. Educational and AI-Assisted Content</h2>
        <p>
            Articles published on this website are intended for educational and
            informational purposes. Some visual elements such as illustrations
            or banners may be generated using AI tools to support explanations
            and design.
        </p>

        <p>
            AI tools may also assist with editing or formatting of content, but
            all articles are reviewed before publication.
        </p>

        <h2>4. Cookies and Tracking</h2>
        <p>
            Currently, this website does not use cookies for advertising,
            behavioral tracking, or personalization. We do not use services such
            as Google Analytics, Facebook Pixel, or other third-party tracking
            tools at this time.
        </p>

        <h2>5. External Links</h2>
        <p>
            ImpulseLog may contain links to external websites for references or
            additional resources. We are not responsible for the privacy
            practices, policies, or content of those external websites.
        </p>

        <h2>6. Policy Updates</h2>
        <p>
            This Privacy Policy may be updated occasionally to reflect
            improvements or changes in website functionality. Any updates will
            be posted on this page along with the revised date.
        </p>

        <h2>7. Contact</h2>
        <p>
            If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, you can reach
            us through the
            <a href="/contact">Contact Page</a>.
        </p>

        <!-- <p><strong>Last Updated:</strong> March 2026</p> -->
    </div>
</BaseLayout>
